  "description": {
    "zh": "霰弹枪？好吧，出于某种原因，那里所有的匪徒都喜欢这些东西，真可惜……对你们PMC来说。总之，我需要收集一点数据，而你是完成这类任务的完美人选，你之前证明过了，是吧？很高兴我能依靠你，嗯。\n\n我会再次把这个任务分成两部分，你会从简单的开始，这些武器都没有使用起来很复杂，甚至不贵。关于这些武器的一点是，它们能彻底摧毁任何没有护甲的东西，而猜猜谁 mostly 不穿护甲到处跑——SCAV。听起来很有趣，对吧？至少对你是这样，你的目标会很难与你对抗，当然……你想干掉谁都行，都会算数，毕竟击杀就是击杀。我不是想在这里欺骗系统，我的朋友。\n\n说到欺骗系统，想要个样品吗？我的一些掠夺者最近找到了这些，但他们没人用霰弹枪，所以我觉得把它们给你是完美的，当然是免费的。所以，你为什么还在这里，捍卫者？责任在召唤，塔科夫的街道不会自己清理干净。",
    "en": "Shotguns? Alright then, for some reason all the bandits out there love these things, what a pity... For you PMCs. Anyway, I need a bit of data collected, and you're the perfect one for this kind of task, you proved that before, yeah? Glad I can rely on you, mhm.\n\nI'll split this task into two parts again, you will start off simple, none of these weapons are complicated to use, or even expensive. One thing about these weapons is that they absolutely annihilate anything without armor, and guess who mostly runs around unarmored - Scavs. Sounds fun, right? For you at least, your targets will have a hard time fighting you, sure... Take down whoever you want, it will count, after all a kill is a kill. I'm not trying to cheat the system here my friend.\n\nSpeaking of cheating the system, care for a sample? A few of my looters found those recently, but none of them use shotguns, so I thought it would be perfect to give them to you, on the house of course. So, why are you still here, champion? Duty is calling, Tarkov's streets won't clean up themselves."
  },
